body:
I'm using Verilator 5.006 from Arch Linux repo

To reproduce:
```
// b.sv
interface AXI_BUS;
  logic         aw_id;
endinterface

module test(input id_i, output id_o);	
  AXI_BUS m_axi;
  assign m_axi.aw_id = id_i;
  assign id_o = m_axi.aw_id;
endmodule
```
```
verilator --trace --binary b.sv -O0
```

Note that `-O0` is necessary to produce this internal error.
